[h3 
	" Introduction
	$LF
	[a id=heading-10 
	]a
]h3
[p 
	"These are 
	(__wikiLink|/Morimoto|Morimoto)
	"'s comments of his world-famous
	$LF
	[a class=intlink href=/668M 
		"SMB3 tool-assisted speedrun
	]a
	", "timeattack".
	$LF
	"The comments originally appeared on his webpage,
	$LF
	"which no longer exists but can be found in the Internet Archive at:
	$LF
	"http://web.archive.org/web/20040403201057/http://soramimi.egoism.jp/emu.htm
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This is my translation of his comments, translated in January 2006.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"I decided to include this page here because it is part of the site's early history.
	$LF
	"Do note that by now, his movie has been surpassed plenty of times,
	$LF
	"with the 
	[a class=intlink href=/342M 
		"newest version
	]a
	" being half a minute faster than his movie.
	$LF
	"More information about the topic can be found in our 
	[a class=intlink href=/ArticleIndex 
		"article
	]a
	" pages.
	$LF
]p
